DEMO is up and running at http://dev.bold-it.com/acro/game.php

SETUP
Host these files on your web server

MySQL/PubNub:
In constants.php, change the PubNub subscription and publish keys to your account keys.
The default MySQL connection is root@localhost, no password.  Change this if necessary

Twilio:
Purchase a number, point the SMS to GET sms.php

HOW TO PLAY
Point a web browser to game.php.  A 3-7 letter acronym will be generated for you.
Players make up a phrase that starts with the letters of the acronym, in order.  Players text the phrase to the Twilio number to be presented.  Matching entries will be displayed on the screen.
Players then get to vote on which they judge to be the best.  Text the ID number on the left to increment that entry by 1 vote.